<L>__{exterior military drill field cuxhaven day}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{our passage was very favorable, and in two days we landed at cuxhaven, and before i had been a month in the electorate, i was transported into a tall and proper young soldier, and, having a natural aptitude for military exercise, was soon as accomplished at the drill as the oldest sergeant in the regiment.}
<A>__{various cuts. roderick learning the soldierly arts, musket drill, manual of arms, bayonet, marching.}
